column5: Finally got a chance to get here....and it's amazing.Here is one photo....more to come.Fishing is outstanding!
Congratulations on finally making it to LOTW. You won't find a better camp anywhere, and you have found a top notch camp owner and operator in Jared. Enjoy your stay.
Don't forget to try out the crappies! Bill
Really?Wish I had a chance to meet you.Looks like you had good luck too.This place is AWESOME!!

Well from your picture you look like the person I talked briefly to on the dock.We just left Saturday. We were there for a week. We were staying in the cabin just left of the dock next to the fish cleaning house. We were the group with our own boats.
Might have been then.......maybe at the liars bench.Looks like you had a great trip!
Was a pleasure having you both. Thanks for the pictures!
